 {"id":"asupersync-2gftc","title":"[WEDGE] FrankenLab CLI: frankenlab run scenario.yaml","description":"Build the FrankenLab CLI tool that runs test scenarios from YAML files. Command: frankenlab run scenario.yaml. Behavior: (1) Parse and validate scenario YAML against JSON Schema, (2) Set up participants with initial state, (3) Initialize deterministic scheduler with seed, (4) Execute scenario with fault injection per schedule, (5) Check assertions, (6) Output results as JSON or human-readable. Additional commands: validate, replay, minimize, compare. Exit codes: 0=pass, 1=assertion failure, 2=scenario error. Must produce clear, actionable error messages. TRACING / LOGGING SPECIFICATION: Span: cli::run with scenario_file, seed, command. Span: cli::validate with scenario_file. Span: cli::replay with trace_file. Span: cli::minimize with scenario_file, strategy. DEBUG: CLI argument parsing: command={cmd}, args={args_json}. INFO: frankenlab {command} started: scenario={file}, seed={seed}. INFO: frankenlab {command} completed: exit_code={code}, duration_ms={ms}, assertions_passed={p}, assertions_failed={f}. WARN: scenario completed with warnings: warning_count={n}, warnings=[{warning_msgs}]. ERROR: scenario execution failed: error={err}, at_step={step}, virtual_time_ms={vt}. ERROR: CLI usage error: {message} (must include suggestion for fix). Metrics: cli_execution_total (counter by command and exit_code), cli_execution_duration_ms (histogram by command), cli_assertions_total (counter by result=pass|fail).","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T09:21:09.781021657Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-14T01:43:29.231422185Z","closed_at":"2026-02-14T01:43:29.231276404Z","external_ref":"bd-1hu19.4","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["cli","frankenlab","wedge"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-2gftc","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1nf8z","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:30:09Z","cre